{"tid":1200511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[簡單教學] 緊急disable手機嘅touch id, face id等生物認證","createTime":"2019-06-10T18:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:10:02.000Z","uid":86943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9efc916be495336d5694b5d14904c39b38345d02","tid":1200511,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:25:09.000Z","msg":"相信大家都有聽過，俾狗拉咗之後被逼解鎖，而大家其實喺有唔解鎖嘅權利嘅<br />\n<br />\n為咗維護自己嘅權利，跟住落嚟教大家一個緊急情況下disable哂生物認證嘅方式<br />\n<br />\n我哋要做嘅唔喺熄機，因為熄機，好多時都係要望住個mon先做到，而 forced reboot就可以一隻手喺褲袋入面渣住部手機都做到<br />\n<br />\nAndroid: 音量向上+開關<br />\n<br />\nIOS: <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2v35SQO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2v35SQO.png&h=85b72413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kQWnU39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkQWnU39.png&h=a7981106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G74s6aQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG74s6aQ.png&h=b1cba7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請對號入座，事先練習好唔望住都可以噤到呢set制<br />\n<br />\n喺重開之後，手機只能透過輸入密碼解鎖，而你喺可以拒絕解鎖嘅<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家"},{"pid":"8002cd4334a2c24c016b4ac5aca44f556fb0921a","tid":1200511,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"Android P 已經直接喺power menu 內置shortcut<br />\n叫做lockdown，噤咗之後就會force你用圖形/pin解鎖"},{"pid":"fef9ed3046db502baec528f77d11bfa1b809e8ec","tid":1200511,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:27:10.000Z","msg":"P 之前嘅機可以直接reboot<br />\nreboot完之後第一次解鎖一定要用 pin/ 圖形"},{"pid":"ea892f8624eaad3589944bf1b4a346e65917edfb","tid":1200511,"uid":86943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8002cd4334a2c24c016b4ac5aca44f556fb0921a","tid":1200511,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:26:36.000Z","msg":"Android P 已經直接喺power menu 內置shortcut<br />\n叫做lockdown，噤咗之後就會force你用圖形/pin解鎖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"要望mon有難度，俾人拉咗應該唔會俾你用手機"},{"pid":"66263c482d52e10b1711bd4dde79eb53a9c58c2e","tid":1200511,"uid":10293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:28:48.000Z","msg":"如果真係唔記得 直接五下lock button<br />\n佢會打去sos 你取消返就ok"},{"pid":"2e69a750f4e071ce2d40aa7492e399b19db57e94","tid":1200511,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"出發前直接set左先啦<br />\n<br />\n到時又急又亂未必有時間同未必記得咁做"},{"pid":"4b6938f44268245c2032088ee3d6bb7b562caf2c","tid":1200511,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2e69a750f4e071ce2d40aa7492e399b19db57e94","tid":1200511,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"出發前直接set左先啦<br />\n<br />\n到時又急又亂未必有時間同未必記得咁做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:32:02.000Z","msg":"一隻手㩒到，唔駛著mon的"},{"pid":"9b6c859ee23db36f37a91c6672055cacf3471166","tid":1200511,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"請廣傳"},{"pid":"648cd0336b73b9231d12abc550a3263c72157e91","tid":1200511,"uid":3893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:36:47.000Z","msg":"iPhone 用家連㩒5下 lock制<br />\n出sos之後 就會轉左一定要入密碼先unlock到"},{"pid":"d215dca3e574e6f12fcf0783bd49ef15ce939823","tid":1200511,"uid":50835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/at1y1Nk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fat1y1Nk.jpg&h=282257f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d58906eaca7ffaf9100596d96f0f994061e91563","tid":1200511,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e4150cead1dbc272583aacf2cb42a87cf4e27a","tid":1200511,"uid":10293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b69